CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 30, 1949, pg. 4, reads: "Religious Services for the late Charlie Williams were conducted at Ebenezer Church, Monday, with the Rev. Robert Johnson officiating. On the left, the body is being borne from the church... - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Pallbearers carrying light colored casket of Charlie Williams through crowd of women and men, for funeral at Ebenezer Baptist Church
